-- Clínica Dental El Bosque - English-Speaking Dental Clinic in Villaviciosa de Odón
('Clínica Dental El Bosque', 'Dental', 'English-speaking dental clinic in Villaviciosa de Odón (Madrid area) with over 50 years of experience serving international patients and expats. Located in the El Bosque commercial center, the clinic offers comprehensive dental care with a professional multidisciplinary team led by Dra. Ángela Prieto. They specialize in oral surgery, implantology, cosmetic dentistry, and orthodontics including Invisalign. Services include dental implants, teeth whitening, dental veneers, endodontics (root canal treatment), orthodontics (braces), conservative dentistry, gum disease treatment, dentures, crowns, and 24-hour emergency dental services. The clinic is committed to responsible, high-quality dentistry with a close and trusting approach to patients. All services available in English and Spanish. Modern facilities ensuring painless and careful treatment. Conveniently located near Boadilla del Monte in the west of Madrid. Opening hours: Mon/Wed/Thu 10am-6pm, Tue 10am-8pm, Fri 10am-4pm.', 'C. Duero, 37, Local 13, 28670 Villaviciosa de Odón', 'Villaviciosa de Odón', 'Madrid', '+34 916 167 034', 'info@clinicadentalelbosque.com', 'https://clinicadentalelbosque.com/en/', true, false, true, false, NOW(), NOW());
